Package: raku-pathtools
Architecture: all
Depends: rakudo, ${misc:Depends}
Description: General purpose file system utility routines
 Provides system utility routine for Raku
 .
 ls - List file/directory (recusively is possible)
 rm - Remove file/directory (recusively is possible)
 mkdirs - Create directories
 mktemp - Create temp file/directory
 tmppath - Generate unique path (the name is time-based)
